{"tid":37640,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[學生資助]同時申請免入息同資助會點","createTime":"2016-12-13T12:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T16:23:11.000Z","uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"87d68fc29ec0676b6eedd85f5c2234380d020bb6","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"免入息批左我，資助仲未<br />\n<br />\n但係可以嘅話我都唔想借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以而家諗緊等資助好定免入息好<br />\n<br />\n想問其實資助批左係咪會自動同我還左免入息條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2177f69f598e5c119ed12560b450cce07362fe33","tid":37640,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c407b1f29c056bc51a57ec3c9fd94e1234071852","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:43:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巨巴真係mon 著連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117ede75d86c6322d540799c31d4a2e0121beef6","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"Help<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ede6dd798f96e9bba8dd5fbb53f17fdc3f76e6b","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123d249683559b32321