normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbc21bdb46d4b138d6e66faaa516d81bfcbd985","tid":37640,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"正路如果你夠窮拎到gran loan就唔駛申請免入息㗎啦啵"},{"pid":"9789e14be283a8f7c0049a83b1068fc14053d313","tid":37640,"uid":26180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>免入息批左我，資助仲未<br />\n<br />\n但係可以嘅話我都唔想借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以而家諗緊等資助好定免入息好<br />\n<br />\n想問其實資助批左係咪會自動同我還左免入息條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇記錯既話，兩樣野獨立計<br />\n但如果你讀緊書既話，免息果到可以畢業後先開始還"},{"pid":"6a35182df93b413da139c60ceada8e0719d1faa7","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正路如果你夠窮拎到gran loan就唔駛申請免入息㗎啦啵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚資助有機會唔批<br />\n<br />\n所以申請埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我而家嘅情況係咪可以等Grant loan 就得<br />\n<br />\n利申：夠窮"},{"pid":"1b904ac340c6afa2d7cb253f7bd1a3ab26369896","tid":37640,"uid":18448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:35:39.000Z","msg":"好似係批完免入息<br />\n跟住再批埋grant loan比你<br />\n咁免入息個條數就會改成grant loan"},{"pid":"43241ebda26bb5311aa9ee6f77a2cf53deb1a6f3","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>免入息批左我，資助仲未<br />\n<br />\n但係可以嘅話我都唔想借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以而家諗緊等資助好定免入息好<br />\n<br />\n想問其實資助批左係咪會自動同我還左免入息條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇記錯既話，兩樣野獨立計<br />\n但如果你讀緊書既話，免息果到可以畢業後先開始還</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係如果免入息批左1萬比我，資助都會照批1萬？<br />\n<br />\n咁未有double 嘅錢囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a668935b884a3c0eecbb85faa44b8a2a95331e4","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似係批完免入息<br />\n跟住再批埋grant loan比你<br />\n咁免入息個條數就會改成grant loan</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條上面位巴打又話獨立...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591ba618f470d34462bb9e59b6018a89054bb929","tid":37640,"uid":3527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:40:19.000Z","msg":"未試過2樣一齊申請，一向拎全資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有朋友拎半資+免入息，應該係獨立計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb83a4cc4a2efb955036986cd5c03bcb34172b2","tid":37640,"uid":26180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>免入息批左我，資助仲未<br />\n<br />\n但係可以嘅話我都唔想借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以而家諗緊等資助好定免入息好<br />\n<br />\n想問其實資助批左係咪會自動同我還左免入息條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇記錯既話，兩樣野獨立計<br />\n但如果你讀緊書既話，免息果到可以畢業後先開始還</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係如果免入息批左1萬比我，資助都會照批1萬？<br />\n<br />\n咁未有double 嘅錢囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都係兩樣野都申請，咁批左全額資助比我，同時都批左免入息。因為資助夠我用，所以就冇要免息果個。<br />\n其實你應該睇下資助批唔批先，因為免入息基本上一定批。"},{"pid":"9c26689bedfe42068311867bd0df6a84dcb3b29c","tid":37640,"uid":45471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"你批到個grant會扣落d loan到。<br />\n<br />\n如果批唔到grant就要全loan，唔想再借既就上學資cut左佢。<br />\n<br />\n利申：有loan等緊grant"},{"pid":"56ccf39c00a5e851c2981713084595c5f4568764","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未試過2樣一齊申請，一向拎全資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有朋友拎半資+免入息，應該係獨立計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇返學資處話會因應資助調整免入息<br />\n<br />\n係咪姐係資助嘅錢會抵消免入息"},{"pid":"a112868523c7385ea1871b92b62c3a08660f9069","tid":37640,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"一句講曬 你唔會收到兩筆學費嫁<br />\n就算grant俾唔曬你 loan都會借埋尾數你<br />\n所以一批你你個免入息應該會失效<br />\n好少話又要借grant loan又要借免入息"},{"pid":"1da414c68e4f4d28c5135957fc4ace33b81183c9","tid":37640,"uid":18448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好似係批完免入息<br />\n跟住再批埋grant loan比你<br />\n咁免入息個條數就會改成grant loan</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條上面位巴打又話獨立...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該咁講<br />\n申請曬兩個<br />\n政府會根據你家庭經濟狀況批<br />\n1.如果入息唔過政府要求，grant loan實會批比你，但時間上non mean啲錢會比較早入你袋，等grant 出咗之後，non-mean條數就會轉做grant =唔洗還<br />\n2.正如頭先個位巴打講，佢朋友non mean同grant各一半，可能係佢家庭經濟狀況來睇，政府只能批一半grant比佢，而另一半學費就會以non mean比佢"},{"pid":"e66dccc0768381cd7856283ab43ee6408672f883","tid":37640,"uid":18448,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:48:06.000Z","msg":"小弟窮撚 四年全grant<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8bbfde1fc487e80ef79a8b0da81322e8037bfb","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇記錯既話，兩樣野獨立計<br />\n但如果你讀緊書既話，免息果到可以畢業後先開始還</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n姐係如果免入息批左1萬比我，資助都會照批1萬？<br />\n<br />\n咁未有double 嘅錢囉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都係兩樣野都申請，咁批左全額資助比我，同時都批左免入息。因為資助夠我用，所以就冇要免息果個。<br />\n其實你應該睇下資助批唔批先，因為免入息基本上一定批。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家就等緊...<br />\n<br />\n但係免入息又21號截止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過佢都話可以截止後交嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffcd876c468f965bd61b00d157c6a2a690df93c","tid":37640,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似係批完免入息<br />\n跟住再批埋grant loan比你<br />\n咁免入息個條數就會改成grant loan</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條上面位巴打又話獨立...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該咁講<br />\n申請曬兩個<br />\n政府會根據你家庭經濟狀況批<br />\n1.如果入息唔過政府要求，grant loan實會批比你，但時間上non mean啲錢會比較早入你袋，等grant 出咗之後，non-mean條數就會轉做grant =唔洗還<br />\n2.正如頭先個位巴打講，佢朋友non mean同grant各一半，可能係佢家庭經濟狀況來睇，政府只能批一半grant比佢，而另一半學費就會以non mean比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據我了解grant loan唔係都有分兩part<br />\n一part grant就唔駛還 <br />\n一part loan就係低息地還<br />\n<br />\n政府批錢既容易程度順次序應該係non mean&gt;loan&gt;grant<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指教"},{"pid":"9f2efc930577b4b2faa53af097969064a3598c8c","tid":37640,"uid":22833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T15:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><bl