mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我期待緊我有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：單親</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我都單親仲有個細佬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母份人工高得滯但又未係好有錢搞到得non mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同單親有關咩？ 我見full grant既話 生活費應該都接近一皮，其他照%派發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能單親易D full grant所以有哩個錯覺"},{"pid":"2a4702494eed54424b676f325ae64e516d4101cd","tid":37640,"uid":33433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我都單親仲有個細佬都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老母份人工高得滯但又未係好有錢搞到得non mean<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同單親有關咩？ 我見full grant既話 生活費應該都接近一皮，其他照%派發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能單親易D full grant所以有哩個錯覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂full grant 嘅生活費係咪姐係果5000幾蚊學習津貼？"},{"pid":"11945413fbda1847dc0ef556757e866bdcc4a03a","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n同單親有關咩？ 我見full grant既話 生活費應該都接近一皮，其他照%派發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁可能單親易D full grant所以有哩個錯覺</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所謂full grant 嘅生活費係咪姐係果5000幾蚊學習津貼？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該生活費還生活費"},{"pid":"e2cf3b5c76e760d17d82a718683c9647c8e2e256","tid":37640,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"梗係等埋先<br />\n可以Grant+mean loan+non mean loan 架嘛"},{"pid":"719e01347cea56f0c002b4250ff13d86a055197f","tid":37640,"uid":18521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係等埋先<br />\n可以Grant+mean loan+non mean loan 架嘛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我grant 就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n主要係唔想借錢"},{"pid":"b925b93b941634281797857a50179aad867e8e30","tid":37640,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好似係批完免入息<br />\n跟住再批埋grant loan比你<br />\n咁免入息個條數就會改成grant loan</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但條上面位巴打又話獨立...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該咁講<br />\n申請曬兩個<br />\n政府會根據你家庭經濟狀況批<br />\n1.如果入息唔過政府要求，grant loan實會批比你，但時間上non mean啲錢會比較早入你袋，等grant 出咗之後，non-mean條數就會轉做grant =唔洗還<br />\n2.正如頭先個位巴打講，佢朋友non mean同grant各一半，可能係佢家庭經濟狀況來睇，政府只能批一半grant比佢，而另一半學費就會以non mean比佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據我了解grant loan唔係都有分兩part<br />\n一part grant就唔駛還 <br />\n一part loan就係低息地還<br />\n<br />\n政府批錢既容易程度順次序應該係non mean&gt;loan&gt;grant<br />\n<br />\n有錯請指教</blockquote><br />\n唔批grant比你就一定無得借grant, grant loan係連埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}